('Anonymous Homeless Kitty', '/homeless.jpg','This fluffy bundle of love has been homeless for the last three months and it doesn’t seem to get better. “My whole life I’ve been a factory worker in a biscuit making factory. Three meownths ago, I got injured, when my colleague tipped a glass of water on top of me. I lost my job cuz I could no longer do the physical labor, and got evicted because I couldn’t pay rent. Since then, I’ve been begging for snacks outside of local neighborhood homes. My health care bills are piling up and my debt keeps growing. Being poor is so expensive.” Poor baby!','#cats #catsofinstagram #evicted #kitty #dc #dcfakemews #poor #beingpoorsucks #fluffy #factory','Poverty', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1487730202306-21b1a371bab0?ixlib=rb-0.3.5&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9&s=1f58b23d5fefef6aa469eed5406a745e&auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&q=60', 1),
('Mason', '/mason.jpg','Meet Mason! This sentimental Sphynx dreams of a purrgressive world where we all abide by the principals of “One Love” and “No Hair, Don’t Care.” As a self-identified nudist, he has no time for the toxic world of body shaming and back stabbing haunting our nation. “Strip away your insecurities! Strip away your fur coats! What’s inside is beautiful,” he cries', '#nude #sphynxcat #dcfakemews #nudist #nohairdontcare #cats #catsofinstagram #nomorebodyshaming #loveyourself #onelove #dccats #lovecats', 'Purrsitive Body Image', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1487730202306-21b1a371bab0?ixlib=rb-0.3.5&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9&s=1f58b23d5fefef6aa469eed5406a745e&auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&q=60', 1),
