('Chuck', '/chuck.jpg','Chuck had always identified as a “nice cat.” “Nice cats finish last,” they’d say, and he believed it. After years of finishing last, Chuck became bitter and started spending all of his time on the r/niceguys reddit. He fed off of the internet trolls. “Why won’t any females mount me??” He would cry into the depths of the internet. Then one day, Chuck had an epiphany. “Why don’t I try LISTENING to the females around me,” he thought to himself. Since then, Chuck has gotten off reddit and into the playing field. He’s got ladies mounting him left and right! Congrats, Chuck', '#reddit #niceguy #nicecat #niceguysfinishlast #chuck #chucky #philly #dccats #catsofinstagram #fatcat #dcfakemews #realnews #windowcat #reddit #redditnicecats #redditniceguys', 'Internet Neutrality', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1499187817214-70f75289a676?ixlib=rb-0.3.5&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9&s=b63a505fb192eb07a2e7548e4b95b81a&auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&q=60', 4),
