('Twix', '/twix.jpg','Twix wants to talk about meowntal health... and we all should want to talk about it! “From depression to PTSD; From anxiety to OCD; modern society throws a lot of squeaky toys in our direction- these things may appear nice, but they’re annoying as hell. The 9-5, 5 day workweek was created by Type-A kitties, while most cats are meant to sleep all day. Social media and video games furrequently produce enough stimulation and trauma to make any feline dash under the couch. Not only that, but our diets of hormones and chemicals make us feel horrible about ourselves. Shit, I’m named after a candy bar! How can anyone be meowntally healthy in such a sick society?? Take me back to days of napping in the sun and fending for my own mice. I’d trade that for a full time job any day!”', ' #mentalhealth #meowntalhealth #normalizeit #dccats #catsofinstagram #greeneyes #tortoiseshellcat #dccitycats #newyork #nyc #newyorkcats #twix #candy #sunshine #naps #vacation #mice', 'Meowntal Health', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519373069499-b54fc6ab1802?ixlib=rb-0.3.5&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9&s=f61e540c4eb0f57542bcfa1e8305acde&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1052&q=80', 1),
