('Vanna', '/vanna.jpg','She may look like a delicate beauty, but underneath her soft exterior lies a fierce femeownist and abortion advo-cat. Hailing from a small midwestern town where sex-ed meant abstinence, Vanna never learned about safe and effective birth control. “As a one year old kitten, I became pregnant. My parents expected me to get meowied, but I refused, so my parents kicked meowt and I was left on the streets. I was pregnant with six kittens, unable to afford food, let alone abortion! My kittens were born in a box behind a farm. Everyone LOVES kittens, but kittens grow up to be cats. And poor cats whose parents can’t afford eduCATion and shelter grow up to eat your garbage, and no one likes that. With luck, my babies were soon adopted! It took me another year to find my furrever family, since no one is pro-life for real adult cats, but now I’m happy!” Wow Vanna. I think we know some humans who can relate!','#abortion #proabortion #safeabortions #sexed #dccats #catsofinstagram #whitecats #dcfakemews #chicago #chicagokitty #chicats #kittens #healthcare #progress #adoptdontshop #adopt #vannawhite', 'Lady Cat Rights', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1513538318453-d0cc70acc86d?ixlib=rb-0.3.5&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9&s=f6a18afb60eaea7ba2fdcccea5d0edc6&auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&q=60', 1),
